  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed side extension by virtue of its design, scale, bulk and massing would represent an incongruous addition to the host building and streetscene and would have an unacceptable detrimental impact on the character and appearance of the host building, the streetscene and the wider Tufnell Park Conservation Area. The proposal is contrary to policies D4, D11, D22, D26 and D27 of the Islington Unitary Development Plan 2002, policy CS9 of the Islington Core Strategy 2011, policies 7.4, 7.6 and 7.8 of the London Plan 2011 and the guidance contained in the Islington Urban Design Guide SPG, the Islington Conservation Area Design Guidelines SPG, and the NPPF."
